videos.headline: Bright gets Utah State on the board with 4-yard score
videos.description: Gerold Bright takes the handoff and runs up the middle for a 4-yard touchdown to give Utah State a 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bright gets Utah State on the board with 4-yard score) 2019/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kent State WR takes off helmet after scoring long TD
videos.description: Kent State's Dustin Crum airs it out deep to Isaiah McKoy who catches the ball in stride and scores a 78-yard touchdown. McKoy gets a unsportsmanlike penalty for taking his helmet off in the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kent State WR takes off helmet after scoring long TD) 2019/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kent State gets INT off big hit
videos.description: Utah State's Jordan Love throws to Taylor Compton who brings in the ball, but gets hit by a defender, allowing the ball to be intercepted by Utah State's Mandela Lawrence-Burke.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kent State gets INT off big hit) 2019/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mariner makes leaping grab for Utah State TD
videos.description: Jordan Love and Siaosi Mariner connect on back-to-back passes, with the second having Mariner battle through contact for a 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kent State retakes lead off big play, 4-yard TD run
videos.description: After Antwan Dixon completes his 53-yard gain for Kent State, Will Matthews punches it into the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kent State retakes lead off big play, 4-yard TD run) 2019/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utah State's Thompkins speeds away for 57-yard TD
videos.description: Utah State's Deven Thompkins runs the fly sweep and gets the ball, finds the edge and speeds away from the defense for a 57-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah State's Thompkins speeds away for 57-yard TD) 2019/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Crum keeps it to extend Kent State's lead
videos.description: On 4th-and-1, Kent State QB Dustin Crum keeps the ball and runs through a seam for a 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Crum keeps it to extend Kent State's lead) 2019/12/20 ESHEET
